paragraphs.title: Raw_Data
paragraphs.text:
cacheTempView(sql="
select distinct tt.orderDate,Channel,deviceType,case when pp.orderId is not null then 'FTU' else 'RTU' end as User,count(distinct tt.subOrderId) as orders,count(distinct tt.guid) as Users
from `temp.order_sd` tt left join `temp.ftu___3` pp on tt.orderId = pp.orderId
where tt.orderDate >= '2022-02-01' and tt.orderDate <> 'orderDate'
group by tt.orderDate,Channel,case when pp.orderId is not null then 'FTU' else 'RTU' end,deviceType
order by orderDate desc
","temp.RawData2")

paragraphs.title: Order_Summary
paragraphs.text:
cacheTempView(sql="
select distinct orderDate, sum(orders)  as SD_Orders,
sum(case when Channel = 'FB Channel' then orders else null end) as FB_Orders, 
sum(case when Channel = 'Google Channel' then orders else null end) as Google_Orders,
sum(case when Channel = 'Other Marketing Channels' then orders else null end)  as Other_Marketing_Orders,
sum(case when Channel = 'whatsapp' then orders else null end)  as whatsapp_Orders,
sum(case when Channel = 'SEO' then orders else null end)  as SEO_orders,
sum(case when Channel = 'Direct'  then orders else null end) as Direct_Orders1,
sum(case when Channel in ('FB Channel','Google Channel','Other Marketing Channels','whatsapp')  then Users else null end) as Marketing_Orders
from 
(select distinct orderDate,Channel,deviceType,User,orders,Users from  `temp.RawData2` pp where datediff(current_date(),orderDate) <=30 )raww
group by orderDate
order by orderDate desc
","temp.Order_Summary2")

paragraphs.text:
run(sql="

with a as(
select distinct so.orderId, so.guid, to_date(from_unixtime(so.createdDate/1000)) as date,so.createdDate 
from (select guid,orderId,createdDate,statusCode from `last1200Days(saleOrder)`) so
left join (select orderId,subOrderId from `last1200Days(suborder)`) sb on sb.orderId = so.orderId
left join (select subOrderId,soiShippingPackageId from `last1200Days(fSubordersOms)`) fso on fso.subOrderId=sb.subOrderId
left join (select spShippingPackageId,sphDateShipped from `last1200Days(fShippingPackage)`) fsp on fso.soiShippingPackageId=fsp.spShippingPackageId
where lower(so.statusCode) NOT LIKE '%fld%' and sphDateShipped is not null),

b as(
select * from a where date>='2021-03-01'
),

c as (
select b.* 
from b 
left join a 
on a.guid=b.guid 
and a.orderId<>b.orderId 
and b.createdDate>a.createdDate 
and datediff(b.date,a.date)<=730
where a.orderId is null
)

select distinct date, guid, orderId
from c
where date>='2021-03-01'
order by date desc

",1000)
